@node "sounds" "Sounds"
@{b}@{i}Pronunciation@{ub}@{ui}

@{i}Vowels@{ui}

The Japanese language has five vowels; @{i}a@{ui}, @{i}i@{ui}, @{i}u@{ui}, @{i}e@{ui}, and @{i}o@{ui}. The vowels are
pronounced as follows:

 @{"A" system "C:Dsound Voice:A.snd"}  as in --------->> @{"Aki" system "C:Dsound Voice:aki.snd"} (Autumn)

 @{"kA" system "C:Dsound Voice:ka.snd"} as in --------->> @{"Katana" rx "C:Dsound Voice:Kat~ah~na.snd"} (Sword)

 @{"kI" system "C:Dsound Voice:ki.snd"} as in --------->> @{"Kiru" system "C:Dsound Voice:Kiru.snd"} (Cut)

 @{"U" system "C:Dsound Voice:u.snd"}  as in --------->> @{"Ushi" system "C:Dsound Voice:ushi.snd"} (Cow)

 @{"Ku" system "C:Dsound Voice:ku.snd"} as in --------->> @{"Kuni" system "C:Dsound Voice:kuni.snd"} (Country)

 @{"E" system "C:Dsound Voice:e.snd"}  as in --------->> @{"Eki" system "C:Dsound Voice:eki.snd"}

 @{"Ke" system "C:Dsound Voice:Ke.snd"} as in --------->> @{"Keito" system "C:Dsound Voice:keito.snd"} (Woolen Yarn)

 @{"O" system "C:Dsound Voice:o.snd"}  as in --------->> @{"Ocha" system "C:Dsound Voice:ocha.snd"} (Green Tea)

 @{"Ko" system "C:Dsound Voice:ko.snd"} as in --------->> @{"Kokoro" system "C:Dsound Voice:kokoro.snd"} (Now)

@{i}Consonants@{ui}

Japanese consonants are pronounced about the same as English consonants. One
exception is the Japanese @{i}r@{ui}, which is pronounced like a combination of the
English r and l, with the result being that it is similar to a d sound (like
@{"ra" system "C:Dsound Voice:ra.snd"}).
@endnode

@node "Express" "Essential Expressions"
@{b}Essential Expressions@{ub}

Yes.                             ----->         @{"Hai." system "C:Dsound Voice:Hai.snd"}

No.                              ----->         @{"Iie." system "C:Dsound Voice:Iie.snd"}

That's right.                    ----->         @{"Sou desu." system "C:Dsound Voice:sou.snd"}

Thank you.                       ----->         @{"Arigatou" system "C:Dsound Voice:Arigatou.snd"}

Thank you very much.             ----->         @{"Doumo arigatou gozaimasu." system "C:Dsound Voice:doumo.snd"}

Excuse me.                       ----->         @{"Sumimasen." system "C:Dsound Voice:Sumimasen.snd"}

Good morning.                    ----->         @{"Ohayou gozai masu." system "C:Dsound Voice:Ohayo.snd "}

Good afternoon.                  ----->         @{"Konnichiwa." system "C:Dsound Voice:Konnichiwa.snd"}

Good evening.                    ----->         @{"Konbanwa." system "C:Dsound Voice:Konbanwa.snd"}

Good night.                      ----->         @{"Oyasumi nasai." system "C:Dsound Voice:Oyasumi.snd"}

Good-bye.                        ----->         @{"Sayounara." system "C:Dsound Voice:Sayounara.snd"}

See you later.                   ----->         @{"Sore Jaa, mata" system "C:DSound Voice:sore_ja.snd"}

I understand.                    ----->         @{"Wakari mashita" system "C:DSound Voice:wakari_mashita.snd"}

I don't understand.              ----->         @{"Wakari masen" system "C:DSound Voice:wakari_masen.snd"}

Excuse me.  Could you help me?   ----->         @{"Sumimasen. Onegai shimasu" system "C:DSound Voice:sumimasen_onegai.snd"}

Do you speak English?            ----->         @{"Eigo wa hanase masuka?" system "C:DSound Voice:eigo_wa.snd"}

I'm looking for someone who speaks English.     @{"Eigo no dekiru wa imasuka" system "C:DSound Voice:eigo_no.snd"}
@endnode

@node "Restaurants" "Restaurants"
@{b}Restaurants@{ub}

I would like to order.   -------------------> @{"Chuumon o onegai shimasu." system "C:DSound Voice:chuumon.snd"}

Do you have ....?        -------------------> @{".... wa arimasuka?" system "C:DSound Voice:wa_arimasuka.snd"}

What is this?            -------------------> @{"Kore wa nan desuka?" system "C:DSound Voice:kore_wa_nan.snd"}

How much is this?        -------------------> @{"Kore wa ikura desuka?" system "C:DSound Voice:kore_wa_ikura.snd"}

I will have ....         -------------------> @{".... o kudasai." system "C:DSound Voice:o_kudasai.snd"}

Please give me my bill.  -------------------> @{"Okanjyou o onegai shimasu." system "C:DSound Voice:okanjyou.snd"}
@endnode

@node "Shopping" "Shopping"
@{b}Shopping@{ub}

Please tell me where to go to buy it? -------> @{".... wa doko de kaemasu ka?" system "C:DSound Voice:wa_doko.snd"}

I would like to buy ....             --------> @{".... o kaitai no desuga." system "C:DSound Voice:o_kaitai.snd"}

How much is it?                      --------> @{"Kore wa ikura desuka?" system "C:DSound Voice:kore_wa_ikura.snd"}

I'll take it.                        --------> @{"Kore o kudasai." system "C:DSound Voice:kore_o.snd"}
@endnode

@node "Vehicles" "Vehicles"
@{b}Vehicles@{ub}

I would like to go to .... -------------> @{".... e ikitaino desuga." system "C:DSound Voice:ikitaino.snd"}

Where can I get a ticket for ....?
                                  @{".... yuki no kippu wa dokode kaemasuka?" system "C:DSound Voice:kippu.snd"}

I would like to get on a train for ...
                                  @{".... yuki no densha ni noritainodesuga." system "C:DSound Voice:densha.snd"}

Does this bus go to ....? --------------> @{"Kono basu wa .... e yukimasuka?" system "C:DSound Voice:kono.snd"}

How much is the fare? ------------------> @{"Ryoukin wa ikura desuka?" system "C:DSound Voice:ryoukin.snd"}
@endnode

@node "Asking" "Asking The Way"
@{b}Asking The Way@{ub}

I would like to go to ....  Would you tell me the way?

     @{".... e ikitaino desuga, michi o osiete kudasai." system "C:DSound Voice:michi_o.snd"}

I am lost.  Where am I on this map?

    @{" Michi ni mayoi mashita.  Kono chizu de genzaichi o oshiete kudasai." system "C:DSound Voice:michi_ni.snd"}

Would you show me where .... is?

     @{".... wa doko desuka?" system "C:DSound Voice:wa_doko.snd"}

Where is the nearst ....?

     @{"Ichiban chikaku no .... wa doko desuka?" system "C:DSound Voice:ichiban.snd"}
@endnode

